name: 5pc Cassette Card
description:
We love the mix tape! Remember staying up all night making the perfect "soundtrack of your feelings" for that special someone?...

...makes the perfect card for any music lover in your life.
The artwork is a gocco screen print with a blank space on the front for filling in your mix tape title
(ex."Tom's Birthday Bash 08")

Black ink on black acid & lignin free card stock.
Each card measures Approx 4” x 5.5” and comes with a matching black envelope. Graphite,reg pencil or white colored pencil looks great when filling out these blank cards.

Artwork is hand printed on a gocco press.
Only a limited number are made at a time.
Please convo for international shipping rates.
